snippet.title: Jim Browning
snippet.description:
Tracking and identifying scammers who knock my front door, call me or shove popups onto my computer screen.

** Please do not email me asking for help with hacking issues. I cannot help. I require scammers to connect to MY PC before I have any chance of identifying them **
